from the ambushed laid by the kidnappers on the highway. The kidnappers reportedly took the traveller into the forest after they confirmed that the driver was dead. Vanguard gathered that the kidnappers had contacted the family of the victim for ransom despite killing the driver during the operation. Recalled that an inspector of police attached to Isua Akoko divisional police station was shot dead by unknown gunmen at the same spot and his service gun was taken away. Vanguard News Nigeria Kidnapped cattle dealer in Ajowa-Akoko, Akoko North-West area of Ondo State, Ayo Faseki, has regained his freedom after his family allegedly coughed out N2.5 million ransom. March 10, 2020 In "News" ...Three travellers abducted  By Dayo Johnson Two personnel of the Ondo State Command of the Nigeria Security and Civil Defence Corps (NSCDC) have died in an auto crash along the Ondo-Ore highway in Ondo State. Reports had it that they were returning from the burial ceremony of a mother of one of their… October 31, 2020 In "News" AKURE—FIVE persons including two blood brothers, died weekend after an auto crash in Ikare-Akoko in Akoko Northeast Local Government Area of Ondo State. February 27, 2012 In "News"